## 🎯 Responsive Design

The website is responsive using CSS Media Queries and adapts to:

- Desktop
- Tablet
- Mobile

Responsive improvements include:

- Flexible layouts
- Stacked sections on smaller screens
- Responsive navigation
- Adaptive payment form
- Responsive product gallery

---

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Download or clone the repository.

```
git clone https://github.com/astro-bot16/OIBSIP.git
```

2. Open the project folder.

3. Open `index.html` in your browser.

or

Use the **Live Server** extension in Visual Studio Code.

